    • Method Detail

      • addGroupId

        public static int addGroupId(Buffer groupId,
                             byte[] groupIdToAdd)
        Used to add a two byte identifier to the group ID.
        Parameters:
        groupId - Buffer with any existing groupID information and space to append groupIdToAdd
        groupIdToAdd - two byte ID to append to the groupID contained in groupId buffer
        Returns:
        CodecReturnCodes.INCOMPLETE_DATA if length of groupIdToAdd is less than 2 bytes or CodecReturnCodes.BUFFER_TOO_SMALL if groupId buffer does not have space to add 2 bytes or CodecReturnCodes.SUCCESS if adding of group id is successful.
